<subSubSection pageId="55" pageNumber="56" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="55.[151,1436,152,642]" pageId="55" pageNumber="56">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[198,339,576,602]" pageId="55" pageNumber="56">Etymology.</emphasis>
Named in recognition of the collector, Dr. Robert S. Anderson, entomologist of the Canadian Museum of Nature, and an assiduous collector of litter inhabiting beetles in Central America.
</paragraph>
